(1,'Changer 5.4.1 has been officially released!','5.4.1','','Changer 5.4.1 has been officially released. This release has fixed bugs in Changer 5.4. Users can upgrade to 5.4.1 now.','<p><strong>Debug history</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Fixed Alipay interface.</li>\n<li>Alias can have \"-\" in it.</li>\n<li>Fixed the bug that date was covered by sticky icon on Latest Article page.</li>\n<li>Fixed the js error when add images to articles in Mobile design.</li>\n<li>Fixed the navigation bar of visual editor, which was not able to get correct data.</li>\n<li>Fixed that Changer 5.4 cannot detect mobile client automatically.</li>\n<li>Fixed that files cannot be deleted from BBS.</li>\n<li>Fixed that English product category cannot be edited.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Dowload</strong></p>\n<p>Source code package <a href=\"http://dl.cnezsoft.com/chanzhi/5.4/chanzhiEPS.5.4.1.zip?version=1008\">http://dl.cnezsoft.com/chanzhi/5.4/chanzhiEPS.5.4.1.zip</a></p>\n<p>Windows one-click installation package <a href=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/book/chanzhieps/68.html\">http://www.chanzhi.org/book/chanzhieps/68.html</a></p>\n<p><strong>Document</strong></p>\n<p>Installation <a href=\"http://changerpress.com/book/changermanual/9.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://changerpress.com/book/changermanual/9.html</a></p>\n<p>Upgrade <a href=\"http://changerpress.com/book/changermanual/11.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://changerpress.com/book/changermanual/11.html</a></p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-25 11:08:00','2016-10-25 13:43:58','normal','article','0',193,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(2,'Social login energizes your website!','sociallogin','sociallogin','A website without interaction with its users is not alive. Changer now has social login!\n\n','<p>Most enterprise websites are actually a web page, rather than a site. Because there is no interaction among members of the site, which is dead and has little value. A good enterprise marketing website should have a member mechanism to interact with the site\'s users/customers. However, it is inconvenient to register a separate account for an enterprise website. Therefore, Changer has added social login.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Changer simplifies the registration which only needs a little information from the user. At the same time, Changer also has a built-in third party social login, such as QQ. Go to \"Set\"-&gt;\"Social Login\" and set third party login.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Once set, you can use social login.</p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-25 13:50:00','2016-11-04 11:00:30','normal','blog','0',39,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(3,'Content Management System','cms','','','<h1>Flexible and Various Content Management</h1>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h4>1. Article<br />\n</h4>\nArticle is a basic must-have function for an application. Article function in Changer includes the managment of Article Category, Article List, and Edit/Publish Article.<br />\n<h4><br />\n</h4>\n<h4>2. Blog<br />\n</h4>\n<p align=\"left\">Blog is to present your team to your customers. Through the content your post, the value and concept of your product and service can be publicized.</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><br />\n</p>\n<h4 align=\"left\">3. Contribution</h4>\n<p>Contribution makes viewers more involved with your website. The articles they contribute will enrich the content and increase the activity of the website.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h4>4. Book/Manual</h4>\n<p>Manual in Changer is a Book which can be viewed on the website rather than downloaded to read as an attachment. It is convenient and fast for users to get help documents.</p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-27 10:43:00','2016-10-27 13:14:09','normal','article','0',134,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(4,'Changer Online Mall','mall','','','<h1>Changer Mall increases sales of your online store!</h1>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>1. Produc</strong><strong>t</strong></p>\n<p>Both image and text can be used in product description. Features can be cutomized.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>2. Order</strong></p>\n<p>It is very easy to place an order on Changer Mall and track its status in the backend.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>3. Pay</strong></p>\n<p>Online payment makes transactions easy and fast between the buyer and the seller. Changer has electronic payments, such as Paypal, available, and ensure payment safe and simple.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>4. Shipping</strong></p>\n<p>Add preferred shipping companies and manage your shipment in Changer.</p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-27 10:45:00','2016-10-27 14:23:45','normal','article','0',210,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(5,'Membership Management','','','','<h1>Membership manangement to enhance interaction with users.</h1>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>1. Message and Reply</strong></p>\nLogin is not required to leave a message, which will involve more users to interact with you. Review is required before the message/reply will show on your website, which avoid negative influence to your website.<br />\n<p align=\"left\"><br />\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>2. Forum</strong></p>\n<p>One-click to switch on Forum at the backend and manage boards like managing articles/products.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>3. Reward Points</strong></p>\n<p>Reward points are gained by members through their actions on the website, such as login, leave a message, etc. You can set rules in gaining points and manage it.</p>\n<p><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4. Open login</strong></p>\n<p>Registration is simple in Changer and social login is supported too. Go to backend and set up corresponding entries to third-party social applications.</p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-27 10:47:00','2016-10-27 16:09:03','normal','article','0',89,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(6,'Customization and Visual Editor','','','','<h4></h4>\n<h1>Easy to get started with website design.<br />\n</h1>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h4>1. Visual editor</h4>\n<p>You can edit, drag and delete blocks at the frontend, and check the rendering effect.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>2. Customization and extension development<br />\n</strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\">For developers, your can design in CSS and JS columns with HTML and PHP.</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>3. All sorts of templates<br />\n</strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\">In order to cater to customers from various industries and those with different preferences and needs, Changer Mall offers all sorts of templates in different styles. You can purchase them and download. More will be coming up...</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><br />\n</p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-27 10:47:00','2016-10-27 16:25:55','normal','article','0',117,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(7,'Search Engine Optimization','','','','<h1>Powerful and effective publicization.</h1>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>1. Internal search optimization</strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\">SEO is useful to boost website visits. You can set keywords for articles, products, etc. Sitemap is also available in Changer to guide your viewers and its XML version is helpful to grab contents from your website.<br />\n<strong></strong><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>2. Statistics <br />\n</strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\">Changer has statistics of Pvs and UVs at the backend so to assist administratos to analyze and maintain the website.</p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-27 10:48:00','2016-10-27 16:37:28','normal','article','0',89,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(8,'Security and Social Login','','','','<h1>Safe and reliable system makes user worry free.</h1>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h4>1. Strong security management provides you a solid support<br />\n</h4>\n<p>With the increase of PVs and UVs, website security is a key matter that cannot be ignored. Changer has built-in security manangement to improve webstie security via verification code, filter, white/black list, sensitive words, privilege manangement, etc.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>2. Social login</strong></p>\n<p><strong></strong></p>','original','','','tengfei','tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-27 10:49:00','2016-10-27 13:53:23','normal','article','0',91,'0',0,'','','','0','en'),(9,'Changer business support and license','suport-license','license;businesssupport','','<p>Changer is an open source software. No fee will be charged for using it and no limit is set to use it for business. You can download it from our website and deploy it on your server. If you have any probelm, you can choose,</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Free Technical Support</strong></p>\n<p>Forum: <a href=\"http://changerpress.com/forum/\" target=\"_blank\">http://changerpress.com/forum/ </a></p>\n<p>QQ: id 2692096539 (Download <a href=\"http://im.qq.com/download/\" target=\"_blank\">QQ</a> , an instant message software and search the ID number to add a friend. Then you will have access to talk with our specialists.</p>\n<p>When you post your quesitons on our Forum, please describe your questions as detailed as possible, e.g. posting screenshots. We will try our best to answer them, but a solution is not guranteed, for Changer itself is free and open source.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Or Charged Technical Support</strong></p>\n<p>Installation support: Install the latest Changer in your device by remote support, USD 30 at a time.</p>\n<p>Upgrade support: Upgrade Changer to the latest version by remote assistance, USD 30 at a time.</p>\n<p>Data migration: Migrate data from other system to Changer, fee based on man-hour.</p>\n<p>Customization: Customized development based on Changer, fee based on man-hour.</p>\n<p>Template desigin: Logo, advertisement and template design for your company, fee based on man-hour.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>For other support and s