(1,'Changer Manual','changermanual','changer;manual;','','','book',0,',1,',1,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-19 10:22:58','2016-10-24 16:27:09',0,1,'en'),
(2,'About Changer','aboutchanger','chanzhi;about;changer','','','chapter',1,',1,2,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-19 10:23:37','2016-10-28 10:44:56',0,1,'en'),(3,'About Changer','aboutchanzhi','about;changer;chanzhi','','<h4 class=\"MsoNormal\">About Changer <br />\n</h4>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Changer is an enterprise marketing system developed by Qingdao <em><strong>Nature Easy Soft</strong></em> for small/medium organizations. You can use it to build your official marketing portal to do publicization, business and customer service. Changer has featured \nmodules, such as article, product, forum, comment, member, blog, help. \nIt is comprehensive and practical with simple backend. It can also do SEO by keywords, summary, etc., so it can build a website\n that can be easily found by search engines.</p>\n<h4 class=\"MsoNormal\">What is the meaning of Changer ?</h4>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Chan(蝉) means Cicedas in Chinese which is an auspicious bug in Chinese culture and symbolizes eminence and richness. It fits the scenario that companies are all for profit. We named it Chanzhi/Changer to express our sincere wish that it can help a lot of small/medium organizations to build their own offical websites, and do publization and marketing.</p>\n<h4 class=\"MsoNormal\">Why Changer is developed?</h4>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">When our team develop other open source products, we need a website to promote our products and a system that can provide technical support to our users and users can download easily. We have tried to use other CMS to build such a system, but it needs a lot of cusmization. So we decided to develop such a system for ourselves. When we were doing this, we have found that most websites are built with obsolete technology, so their loading is slow, SEO is not applied, and backend design is obscure. Therefore, through four years\' dealing with our clients and improving our product, we now have Changer as an enterprise portal system to sovle all the problems.</p>\n<h4 class=\"MsoNormal\">Why is Changer an open source?</h4>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Changer is an open source software and welcome business development. It is our belief that open source is the right way to do software and that only being open source can bring mroe vitality to our product and our clients can use it at hteir will.</p>\n<h4 class=\"MsoNormal\">Why you should choose Changer to build your enterprice portal/website?</h4>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You have a lot of options when it comes to choose a tool to building your website, such as Wordpress, Drupal and such open source. Or hire an agent to build it for you, if you have enough budget. So what is so sepcial about Changer?</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">First, Changer is specialized in enterprise portal system.</p>\n<ul><li>Changer is for companies which need marketing websites, so we focus functions on online marketing features. Changer has functions such as article, product, member, comment, help, blog, so to cater to online marketing.</li>\n<li>Changer focuses on SEO. It has functions as keyword management, summary and sitemap. As long as the system supports to rewrite URL, a path that is friendly to search engines can be generated, such as /news/123.html.</li>\n<li>Changer can do statistic analysis. Even there is only a visitor to your website, you will see it from the statistic report.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Secondly, Changer is an open source software.</p>\n<ul><li>Changer is the only enterprise marketing system that is an open source in China.</li>\n<li>Changer Llicense is not strict and it is business friendly. Its code is totally open.</li>\n<li>Changer does not limit businese use, and will not set limits due to the launch of the professional version and fee-based services.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Last but not least, Changer has advanced technology and focuses on user experience.</p>\n<ul><li>Changer uses ZentaocPHP as its framework, of which the struture is designed.</li>\n<li>It has full extensible mechanism, so users can develop their own business system based on Changer. You will find it is eady to reproduce.</li>\n<li>Our team keep studying relavant design philosophy and will improve Changer all the time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Last not not least, Changer has supports.</p>\n<ul><li>Changer is developed by professional open source programmers. We do it as a professional, not just as a hobby.</li>\n<li>Changer team has over ten years experience in open source development and maintenance, as well as in reproduction and supports.</li>\n<li>Changer is open both in codes and team. We will have third party developersrs and agents to join us, so to build a organic system for enterprise marketing.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Choose <em>Changer</em>, choose the right marketing tool!</strong><br />','article',2,',1,2,3,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-19 10:24:23','2016-11-14 15:58:16',267,1,'en'),(4,'How to do marketing in the age of mobile internet?','','mobileinternet;marketing','','<p>In the age of mobile internet, how to do marketing? Among so many social media, such as Wechat (a chat app), Weibo (a micro blog platform), Weidian (a micro online shop), which one we should choose to do marketing? Two of our products, Changer and Ranger (a collaborative system), are our answers to it.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>We beliece that even a small brand should be at your own disposal. Companiess should pay more attention to their branding in the age of mobile internet, when media and users are all scattered. You can have your own websites at their hands, while other resources are at the third party\'s. Some comoanies spend a lof of efforts on building their service on third party website, but what is at your hands? An ID maybe? Once those third party platforms are gone, there is almost nothing left for you.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Therefore, we would like to help your integrate PC, social media, and mobile phone on Changer. Changer, as a content and marketing management system, can easily deliver contents to all kinds of marketing platforms, and meanwhile gather the users and feedback from all those platforms. You can also interact with your customers on Changer, while they can purchase and consult about products/service with you. You can either use Changer to do all this on your PC, or on your mobile phones and social media applications.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',2,',1,2,4,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-19 14:43:28','2016-10-28 14:14:30',108,2,'en'),(5,'Changer License','changerlicense','','','Z PUBLIC LICENSE 1.2<br />\n<br />\nAuthorization<br />\n<br />\nZ PUBLIC LICENSE, also known as ZPL Agreement, is drafted by QingDao \nNature Easy Soft Network Technology Co,LTD. (www.cnezsoft.com).<br />\nAnyone can use the agreement to publish open source software, and modify\n the blank underlined part of the following text of the agreement \naccordingly.<br />\nNo other text of the agreement shall be changed. QingDao Nature Easy \nSoft Network Technology Co,LTD has the final authority to interpret the \nterms of the agreement.<br />\n<br />\nPreface<br />\n<br />\nChanzhi/Changer EPS (Hereinafter referred to as \"the software\") developed by \nQingDao Nature Easy Soft Network Technology Co,LTD (hereinafter referred\n to I). I\'m entitled to all copyright of the software.<br />\nThe software is released as open source software. You are authorized to \nuse the software as long as you are in compliance with this agreement.<br />\nBy installation of the software, you agree that a contractual relationship between you and me is automatically established.<br />\nYou are obliged to fully comply with all the terms of this agreement \nunless you choose to stop using the software or you have signed \nadditional contracts with me.<br />\n<br />\nMy Contact:<br />\n<br />\nMobile：&nbsp; 15588665232<br />\nEmail：&nbsp;&nbsp; co@chanzhi.org<br />\nQQ：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2692096539<br />\nWeibo：&nbsp;&nbsp; easysoft<br />\nAddress： Room 1106, Block C, Dong