','2016-10-31 08:14:29',87,1,'en'),(9,'Source Code Installation','','sourcecode','','<h4>1. System requirements</h4>\n<ul><li>PHP 5.0+ with pdo, pdo_mysql，json, pcre;</li>\n<li>MySQL 4.0+;<br />\n</li>\n<li>Apache or Nginx.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2. Upload source code</h4>\n<p>Download .zip source code installation package from our website and unzip it, you will have two directories which are named www and system. Upload source code to your web server,</p>\n<ul><li>If you manage your server, you can upload the whole directory of Changer to your server and configure Apache/Nginx, and configure your web root direcoty to changer/www.<br />\n</li>\n<li>If your web server is shared space you bought, you need to use FTP to upload what is in Changer/www/ to www/html/web. Then upload the directory of system to www/html/web. The final directory will be as in the screeshot below,</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201311/e143228ae5f95dac9f9c95ee80454091.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h4>3. Start the installation</h4>\n<p>3.1 Start the installation</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Visit your domain at http://domain/install.php. If you set up Changer under secondary directory, you need add secondary path to your domain.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3.2 Check PHP modules and directory privileges</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201311/5ce2cd588d065ded9a116aab3e0967b6.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Note: If there is any problem with modules or direcories, please follow the notice given by the system.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3.3 Configure your database</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201311/0c4770ebe86159aa630d4fa625d60649.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Note: If you have installed Changer before, please check \"clear database\" and then install Changer again.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3.4 Save your configuration document</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201311/274177824a6cfac7314c7e961d2fa5d1.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Note: Changer will save configuration documents for you. However, please manually save your configuration documents to config/my.php. Follow the notice given, if any error cause by privileges.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3.5 Configure admin account</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201311/44b4c146841a5110882180bfd218c232.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3.6 Login Changer backend</p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201311/010941b0b116b444b492ade9b5bdcfec.png\" alt=\"\" /></strong></p>\n<p>Note: It might happen that you are directed to \"Successfully installed\" before you set up admin account, if your php&nbsp;<span>session.save_path is relatively created. Please follow the instructions below to fix it.</span></p>\n<p><span>Open <span style=\"line-height:1.57142857;\">php.ini</span>, find <span style=\"line-height:1.57142857;\">session.save_path</span> and change the pathe to absolute path, such as <span style=\"line-height:1.57142857;\">“\\tools\\xampp\\tmp”. The full path will be <span style=\"line-height:1.57142857;\">“D:/tools/xampp/tmp”</span>. Restart your Apache and it will work. Reference : <a href=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/thread/177.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chanzhi.org/thread/177.html</a></span></span></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',7,',1,7,9,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 09:25:23','2016-10-31 08:14:29',98,2,'en'),(10,'One-Click Installation','oneclickinstallation','one,click','','<p>We also have one-click installation package available.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h4>1. Installation</h4>\n<p>1.1 Download Windows integrated operating system (changer.***.exe) from our website.</p>\n<p>1.2 Double click to unzip it to a root directory of any partition, such asC:\\xampp or D:\\xampp.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201404/f_9e88e6f712f8e8603158203e27fd3689.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1.3 Go to the folder named xampp, and double click start.bat to launch Changer control panel..</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201404/f_c8d860edb5a464502525449ceed4d8d9.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h4><br />\n</h4>\n<h4>2. Start and access Changer</h4>\n<p>2.1 Click \"Start\" to launch Changer service.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201404/f_fc06ff53f3c2047b43120202636d563c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2.2 Click \"Access Changer\" to enter Changer front-end,or enter http://127.0.0.1.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201404/f_000793ddc8192de520767b8a13a3a5bd.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>2.3 The default backend address&nbsp;http://127.0.0.1/admin.php with a default admin accoun \"admin\" and the default password \"123456\". If your default port is not 80, you have to manually add one.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201404/f_2be88524ef67e5a755fd6f0801b2da78.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h4>3. About Changer runtime</h4>\n<p>3.1 The access path to Changer is http://Changer ip adress:port/zentao/.Changer ip adress is the IP address of the machine installed Changer. If the Port is not 80, change it to the actual port you use.</p>\n<p>3.2 Changer control panel will nstall Apache and MySQL, and the service names are apachezt and mysqlzt.</p>\n<p>3.3 This environment is a simplified version og xampp.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h4>4. What if the control panel failed...<br />\n</h4>\n<p>In case you could not lauch the control panel, you can start Changer with control scrpit.</p>\n<p>4.1 Go to xampp\\service.</p>\n<p>4.2 Double click install.bat, then Apache and MySQL will be automatically installed and launched.</p>\n<p>4.3 After you install Changer, there will be port.apache and port.mysql to record the port number of Apache and MySQL. If you want to change the port, please delete the two files and run install.bat again.</p>','article',7,',1,7,10,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 09:25:23','2016-10-31 08:14:29',79,3,'en'),(11,'Update Changer','','update','','<p>Changer\'s release is very often and every version will have bugs fixed and function improved. Therefore, it is strongly recomended that you update your Changer to the latest verson. It is also very easy to update Changer,</p>\n<h4>1. Download the latest source code installation package.</h4>\n<p>1.1 Download .zip source code package from you website. Do NOT downliad the one-click installation package.</p>\n<p>1.2 Unzip the package, and copy it to the directory where you installed Changer before to replace it.</p>\n<p>Fo example, if you installed Changer under c:\\xampp\\chanzhi, replace it with the new version to the same direcroty c:\\xampp\\chanzhi. Do NOT copy it to c:\\xampp\\chanzhi\\chanzhi. If you installed Changer in virtual space, please refer to 1.2 and replace the files there.</p>\n<h4>2. Execute update <br />\n</h4>\n<p>2.1 Access to Changer update program</p>\n<p>For example, if your Changer access path is http://192.168.1.99/, your update path will be http://192.168.1.99/.</p>\n<p>2.2 Create OK file to ensure your permission to update</p>\n<p>Before update, Changer will create a file named OK under&nbsp;chanzhi/www/ to make sure that you have the permission to update Changer.</p>\n<p>Note: For Changer 2.5.1 or higher, no OK file to check permission any more)</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201308/f2f959a22dbe30cf6cf56d6f11d5c525.png\" /></p>\n<p>2.3 Backup database</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201308/e096345d3bf3cbf3555267b8285f0362.png\" /></p>\n<p>2.4 Confirm your current version and click \"Update\".</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201308/fb17f8ebb7433322073f0b265df5d219.png\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',7,',1,7,11,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 09:25:23','2016-10-31 08:14:29',113,4,'en'),(12,'Set Changer Templates','themes','theme','','<strong>Note</strong><ul><li>You need <strong>Zend Guard Loader</strong> to set encrypted template which is purchased on Changer official website). Please refet to <a href=\"http://changerpress.com/book/changermanual/ZendGuardLoader-13.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em>2.6 How to instal Zend Guard Loader.</em></a></li>\n<li>Templates have to be compatible with Changer version. If you use <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.zsite.com/\">Zsite</a>, our online website builder, you don\'t have to purchase any templates.</li>\n<li>If Zend Guard Loader is not installed, or&nbsp; the domain is not the one you setup in Changer, you might not be able to access to your website.</li>\n<li>If you got a notice such as \"Error 500\" or \"Domain Error\", please delete the file which has the same name as your template under <span style=\"font-size:14px;\">changer/system/module/ui/ext/config/</span> on your server, and then uninstall the template at backend. Make sure Zend Guard Loader is installed and domain name is the same as the one you set up in Changer, then install the template again.</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<p>1. You can set up templates for your website in Changer. Changer templates can be purchased on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/theme-browse.html\">Changer official website</a>, or you can click \"Design\" -&gt; \"UI\" -&gt; \"Template\" to design your own template at the backend.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Import templates</p>\n<p><em></em><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201602/f_631a4d0c9ba3b728bb18c68670d48da0.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. Admin privilege will be checked before you import template. Please create and enter certain content as instructed.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201602/f_84b7f8937ad385538da630df748c6942.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>4. Upload .zip package. Once uploaded, you might have to modify certain folder permissions and upload it again as required.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>5. After that, you will be asked to merge modules. Save the default setup, if you don\'t want to merge anything.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201602/f_f895037ab8ecf381b6623972e17dc82b.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>6. You will see template you just install under Theme list.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',7,',1,7,12,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 09:25:23','2016-10-31 08:14:29',87,5,'en'),(166,'Company Information','','','','<p>Go to <strong>Set</strong>-&gt;<strong>Company</strong>-&gt;<strong>Company Information</strong> and add your company information.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_fad5b588475cb897aac093f8f8a4c943.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',163,',1,14,22,163,166,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-12-28 11:27:27','2016-12-28 14:56:32',57,1,'en'),(164,'Points','','','','','chapter',22,',1,14,22,164,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-12-28 11:25:01','2016-12-28 11:25:31',0,3,'en'),(165,'API','','','','','chapter',22,',1,14,22,165,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-12-28 11:25:01','2016-12-28 11:25:31',0,4,'en'),(163,'Company','','','','','chapter',22,',1,14,22,163,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-12-28 11:25:01','2016-12-28 11:25:31',0,2,'en'),(168,'Set Email ','','','','<p>In Changer, you can send Email notifications about any changes. Now let\'s set it.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Login Changer with admin account.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2.Click \"Set\"-&gt;\"API\"-&gt;\"Email\" and enter the Email address the notification will be sent from.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_6aca054a22a16e9fbc6005fb99978d06.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. Add <span>email info such as smtp password. Take QQ email as an example. Turn on smtp service in QQ email. Please note:</span></p>\n<ul><li><span>Smtp server has to be same as your QQ email. For example, your smtp server has to be <span>smtp.qq.com</span>, if you use QQ email.</span></li>\n<li><span>smtp password is the authorization code you received from your email server, not your Email password.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5ffd0d94fb3f2a6b417f60f5516dacb6.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_09f1143d9567617e1eafbc83e8c31843.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>4. Click \"Save\", then your Email is set. Click\"Test\" to check whether you have successfully set your email.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_19c4a0fc36af3bbc68a94ed058910a3f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>P</p>\nThe third party SMTP is listed below.<ul><li>Tencent QQ email (recommended) : smtp.qq.com&nbsp; <em>How to turn on smtp/pop3</em>, click <a href=\"http://service.mail.qq.com/cgi-bin/help?subtype=1&amp;id=28&amp;no=166\" target=\"_blank\">http://service.mail.qq.com/cgi-bin/help?subtype=1&amp;id=28&amp;no=166</a>&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#E53333;\">Note : You have to set security code seperately <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://service.mail.qq.com/cgi-bin/help?subtype=1&amp;&amp;id=28&amp;&amp;no=1001256\">Click here to see how</a></span></li>\n<li><p><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">NetEase 163 email：smtp.163.net </span><em><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">How to turn on smtp/pop3</span></em><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">, click </span><a href=\"http://help.163.com/10/0312/13/61J0LI3200752CLQ.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://help.163.com/10/0312/13/61J0LI3200752CLQ.html</a><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"> Note: <span style=\"color:#E53333;\">You have to set password seperately</span>&nbsp; <a href=\"http://help.mail.163.com/faqDetail.do?code=d7a5dc8471cd0c0e8b4b8f4f8e49998b374173cfe9171305fa1ce630d7f67ac2cda80145a1742516\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"></span></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://help.mail.163.com/faqDetail.do?code=d7a5dc8471cd0c0e8b4b8f4f8e49998b374173cfe9171305fa1ce630d7f67ac2cda80145a1742516\">Click here to see how</a></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Sina free email：smtp.sina.com &nbsp;<span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"></span><em><span style=\"color:#64451D;\">How to turn on smtp/pop3</span></em><span style=\"color:#64451D;\"></span></span>, click <a href=\"http://mail.sina.com.cn/help2/client01.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://mail.sina.com.cn/help2/client01.html</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>Tencent exmail：smtp.exmail.qq.com</li>\n<li>Yahoo free email：smtp.mail.yahoo.cn</li>\n<li>NetEase 126 email：smtp.126.com</li>\n<li>Sohu free email：smtp.sohu.com</li>\n<li>Gmail：smtp.gmail.com</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note:</p>\n<ol><li>Changer do not send emails to the one who is sending email to others, because s/he might receive duplicated emails.</li>\n<li>If\n you use the thrid party email service, such as QQ email or NetEase \nemail, you have to turn on smtp service on the setting page of their \nwebsite.</li>\n<li>Usually all you need to do is to enter your password, \nbecause Changer can detect popular email servers in China and set up for\n you.</li>\n<li>If you got a notice saying that data is not accepted, \nplease chech whether your email server set any limits to sending \nfrequency/security.</li>\n<li>If a notice saying that you cannot connect \nto smtp erver, it usually means that Changer server cannot connect to \nyour email server. So you have to check whether your domain name can be \nresovled, the port is correct, or any firewall block your connection. <br />\n</li>\n</ol>\n<br />','article',165,',1,14,22,165,168,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-12-28 14:37:11','2016-12-29 09:59:20',56,1,'en'),(14,'How to use Changer','','use,employ','','','chapter',1,',1,14,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 17:14:53','2016-08-25 15:32:09',0,3,'en'),(15,'Content','','','','','chapter',14,',1,14,15,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 17:21:58','2016-08-29 08:58:03',0,1,'en'),(81,'Add a book','','','','<p>In Changer, you can write a book for your product/service as a manual. It is convenient for users to know \nthe product/service, and users can refer to it to solve problems.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Login Changer as Admin, and go to \"<strong>CMS</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Book</strong>\"， click \"<strong>Add book</strong>\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_bee3cfb9bbf730ce67723457da141f93.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>3. You will see \"Add a book\" page as shown below.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>You\n must have an alias for your book, which will be a combination of \nletters/numbers. For example, the alias of our Changer manual is \nChangerhelp.</p>','article',78,',1,14,15,78,81,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:23:58','2016-12-23 16:05:29',88,1,'en'),(90,'User Management','','','','','chapter',25,',1,14,25,90,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:16:43','2016-12-27 09:56:43',0,1,'en'),(22,'Set','settings','','','','chapter',14,',1,14,22,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 17:23:11','2016-12-28 11:23:09',0,7,'en'),(23,'UI','UI','','','','chapter',14,',1,14,23,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 17:23:11','2016-12-27 14:35:12',0,5,'en'),(68,'Basic settings','sitesettings','site;settings','','<p>The basic information of a website includes the name of the site, slogan, description, registration number, etc. You have to set\nthose information before you create a website.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"Set\"-&gt; \"Site\"-&gt;\"Basic settings\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_bfb547a0471321c748def2edbbd51366.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Keywords are very important, because it is the main push word. Please set keywords properly.</li>\n<li>Siogan describes what the site is for and it will be shown in the center of the header.</li>\n<li>Site descrition will show in the meta tab of the header, so it is also very important.</li>\n<li>Meta tags have tabs like &lt;meta&gt;&lt;script&gt;&lt;style&gt;&lt;link&gt;.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',49,',1,14,22,49,68,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:43:38','2016-12-28 13:41:08',126,1,'en'),(25,'User','','','','','chapter',14,',1,14,25,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 17:24:41','2016-12-27 09:56:27',0,3,'en'),(26,'Mall','','','','','chapter',14,',1,14,26,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 17:24:41','2016-08-29 08:58:03',0,2,'en'),(97,'Submit an article','','contribution','','<p>Changer 4.6+ has submission which means users can write an article and submit to your website.</p>\n<br />\n<p>1. Go to \"<strong>Set</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Site</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Basic settings</strong>\". Check \"Submission\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5c7587f34434f24f037d4a405f5b76b8.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Once checked, \"<strong>Submission</strong>\" will show on users home by login their accounts. Please note that you have to switch on User feature at the backend to activate \"Submission”.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_b41530a41d104c5c5b529378944109b7.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. Click \"<strong>Submit</strong>\", you will see a page to write your submission. Select the source for your submission. If it is from a website, you can add the link to it. Click \"Submit\" to finish your submission.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://changerpress.com/data/upload/201612/f_6da5ad916581e1ad12ab3f14e2ef3ec7.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Once submitted, you can see your it in \" <strong>Submission</strong>\" and its status can be seen here, and you can edite/ delete it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_40150215a040694032814ee8614fa741.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. Website administrator can go to \"<strong>CMS</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Submission</strong>\", Admin can review and delete users\' submission at backend.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_969fd4c2fe96338057ec9e72047a9789.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"<strong>Review</strong>\", Admin can either <strong>Pass</strong> or <strong>Reject</strong> the sybmission. If Pass, admin can add this submission to related category.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_b940a9f51342088dedf475a400975428.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>4. Users can see the status of the review. Once the submission passed the review, uses cannot edit/delete it. Rejected sumissions can be edited/deleted.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5cf633ecb491e1f830f2afe1b87b4b81.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',79,',1,14,15,79,97,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:29:13','2016-12-26 11:30:39',84,1,'en'),(29,'SEO','','','','','chapter',14,',1,14,29,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-22 17:24:41','2016-12-28 14:05:54',0,4,'en'),(30,'Article','','category;article','','<p>Article content management is a must-have function for a website builder, so Changer has such function. Before adding any content to your website, let us maintain the categories of articles first.</p>\n<h4>1. Login backend</h4>\n<p>Login Changer with admin account, such as 比如http://192.168.1.99/admin.php.</p>\n<h4>2. Start to manage categories</h4>\n<p>Click \"Article\"-&gt;\"Maintain categories\", and the management page will show.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_48e7466283d45d71dc9fd52e93a13504.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h4><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_b7ca9734c4f80aef0e605edc8e46b453.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></h4>\n<p>Note: Category can have alias(no hyphen please) so to be friendly to search engines.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5 categories can be added at the same time. If you want to add more than five, save the first five and add the rest of them.</p>\n<h4>3. Maintain subcategory</h4>\n<p>You can add as many subcategories as you like. Choose a category, click \"add a sub\", then you can maintain the subcategory, and so on so forth.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_e8961a67c56c92cfa854317a8cdca2ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','chapter',15,',1,14,15,30,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-23 09:10:18','2016-08-25 11:22:04',0,1,'en'),(32,'Page','','','','<p>1. Login Changer backend with admin account, and you will see Article page.</p>\n<p>2. You will see the list of your articles and each article has several function buttons to edit the article.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_cd9e7e533ae0d3615bba15eabd791152.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>3. You can add CSS, JS codes to your article. You can also set the top article and whether the category is on the top.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_c06377e13fed51e3b7092d37a4b1b6d4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>4. You can post your articles to your blog/forum via Changer. The default posting time is within 48 hours.</p>\n<p>5. You can set the layout of a certain article.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_8f036640f0572835fafae0b274a0d52d.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>6. You can maintain the attachment of an article.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201602/f_7807cb301b51a5c99828d781f3c85845.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>7. You can maintain the pictures of an article, such as set a pic as its cover.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201602/f_d2ba7a76ca60a180471b29794c9fbcbd.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','chapter',15,',1,14,15,32,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-23 09:10:18','2016-08-25 11:22:04',0,2,'en'),(75,'Edit, Delete and Attach','','','','<p>1. Login Changer as Admin and go to <strong>CMS</strong>-&gt;<strong>Article</strong><strong></strong>, and all articles with different action buttons will display at the right column.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_17557f7b54671e91c66ae13c4b20d5f8.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Click <strong>More</strong> to add CSS, JS code to your article. You can also set the article as sticky and post your articles to your blog/forum via Changer. The default posting time is within 48 hours.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_3f4c49c2f8ccd0cd61c6113f9d8be173.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. Click <strong>Layout</strong> to set the layout of an article.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_d2106216b0dc747b2482050c64bf66f1.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>4. Click <strong>File</strong> to add You can upload the attachment of an article.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_d8962d883b55da7940c6b6841184006a.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>5. Once file is uploaded, you can see the preview of the image, and set it as cover, rename or download it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_1a6c1fbc30020af25253e3627b089efb.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',30,',1,14,15,30,75,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:17:44','2016-12-23 13:39:43',90,3,'en'),(82,'Add chapters to a book','','','','<p>After you add a book, you can create the table of contents for the book/manual. Our design philosphy of Book is to create a \nbook/manual first, then create the directory, and then to \nwrite articles for each chapter. Let\'s see how to set the contents first.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Choose a Book, click \"<strong>Chapter</strong>\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_0db6e0bea2a6020daadc912d622062b2.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>A page will be open for you to add chapter titles. You can choose \"Chapter\" or \"Article\" to be the type of content you are adding.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_002c463c55b3473df1b0f93b538ac405.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',78,',1,14,15,78,82,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:23:58','2016-12-26 10:01:52',87,2,'en'),(83,'Write articles for a chapter','','','','<p>After you create the cintents for chapters. you can start to write articles. Please refer to the relevant chapter to write your articles.</p>\n<p>How to use Changer to publish articles, refer to Chapter <em>3.1.2 Publish articles.</em></p>\n<p>How to edit, delete and attach, refer to Chapter <em>3.1.3 Edit, delete and attach.<br />\n</em></p>','article',78,',1,14,15,78,83,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:23:58','2016-12-26 10:24:21',87,3,'en'),(84,'Book settings','','','','<p>Click <strong>Settings</strong> of a book, you can set the Home of Book, Full Screen and Table of Contents.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Home: You can choose a book or the Book List to show on the homepage of Book.</p>\n<p>Full Screen: Switch on/off full screen display.</p>\n<p>Table of Contents: Set the layout of Table of Contents.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_a576df8355da387e7af2265c8f3909a8.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',78,',1,14,15,78,84,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:23:58','2016-12-26 10:35:02',79,4,'en'),(91,'Comment','','','','','chapter',25,',1,14,25,91,',4,'tengfei','','2016-08-25 13:16:43','2016-08-25 13:18:01',0,2,'en'),(92,'Board','','','','','chapter',25,',1,14,25,92,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:16:43','2016-08-25 13:25:28',0,3,'en'),(94,'Board settings','board','','','<p>Why a Board module is built in Changer, since there are Discuz, Phpwind \navailable already? The answer is that the fundamental value of a board \nis to communicate and to exchange information, which Discuz and Phpwind \nis absolutely not doing that, which can be told by the \namount of valid information from those boards. Therefore, we have a \nsimple Board module in Changer just to provide a handy tool for you to\n communicate with your users.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>First, set up basic information of a forum. At least two levels of boards have to be set before it shows on your website. Login Changer with your admin account, then click <strong>User</strong>-&gt;<strong>Forum</strong>-&gt;<strong>Boards</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5866a9f87dd18e62b0653a25945a0f6f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Manage boards on a separate page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_79bfcc4a37cc4b423db64dcab069f410.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Forum will show on your website like this,</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_a9e0e8238c0b8b122f53faa84e36e3bf.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',92,',1,14,25,92,94,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:21:03','2016-12-27 11:04:50',80,1,'en'),(93,'Review and reply a comment','','','','<p>You can review and reply comments to \ninteract with them, such as offering product information and quotation.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Go to Set-&gt;Site and ceck \"Message\" to turn on the service.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_0dd49af20b83f0cdd1e5de02fe7f5f25.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Users can write a comment on your website. Administrator should \nlogin backend&nbsp; to review and reply those comments. In Changer, the\n default setting of comments is that only the one who writes the comment and \nthe admin can see it. Therefore, admin has to review and approve the \ncomment, so other users can see it too.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Go to User-&gt;Message</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_df462ed8e731e42cda147d4b683b301c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>\"Reply\" means to reply this comment.</p>\n<p>\"Delete\" means to delete this comment.</p>\n<p>\"Pass\" means to approve this comment.</p>\n<p>\"Pass Prev\" to approve this comment and comments written before this one.</p>\n<p>\"Delete Prev\" means to delete this comment and commennts written before this one.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>It\n is the same procedure if you want to edit comments, replies, threads in \nthe Feedback. If you integrate Wechat within Changer, you can check and \nreply Wechat messages in Feedback.</p>','article',91,',1,14,25,91,93,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:19:04','2016-12-26 14:54:09',81,1,'en'),(86,'Product category','productcategory','','','<p>In Changer, you have to add a product category before you manage products.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Login Changer with your admin account, and go to <strong>Mall</strong>-&gt;<strong>Product</strong>-&gt;<strong>Manage Category</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_c38b3485dc765312d91d4b36803a91fb.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2.<strong> </strong>You can add multi-level categories. Product alias is for SEO. Click \"Edit\" to edit category details. You can set the layout for each product category.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_96bf44db53ad02911187042203667d4c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',66,',1,14,26,66,86,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:10:28','2016-12-26 14:34:29',75,1,'en'),(87,'Add a product: basic info','','','','<p>After category is added, you can add products now. You can add product basc info, descriptions and images. Let us start with the basic info.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Login Changer with your admin account and then click \"<strong>Mall</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Product</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Add</strong>\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_acd84222eeb7ae2b19b2c83dd93288d8.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Choose categories and enter product name, alias etc.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_f759d99b4773d76b55ef012849674533.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>1. One Product can belong to several categories.</p>\n<p>2. Alias, keywords and abstract are for SEO.</p>\n<p>3. You can add links from the third party, such as Taobao, Amazon, Ebay etc.</p>','article',66,',1,14,26,66,87,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:10:28','2016-12-26 15:12:43',97,2,'en'),(88,'Add a product: attributions','','','','<p>Go to <strong>Mall</strong>-&gt;<strong>Product</strong> and click <strong>Add</strong>, you can add attributions, such as producr price, origins of products, model, to a product.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_838be23383308a9fc6107fb229edd30b.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can add customized attributions by defining Tags and the values..</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',66,',1,14,26,66,88,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:10:28','2016-12-27 09:45:23',85,3,'en'),(89,'Add a product: images','','','','<p>Images are very important to promote products. It can help \ncustomers know the product&nbsp;better. Let\'s \nsee how to add images to products.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"File\" in the Action of the product list.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_29ca1a195facf36ca7b04030e5b73570.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>A page will show for you to maintain product images, such as add a new image, and set an image as its cover.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_85e9b0027fcf6dce0653368221465051.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>The frontend will show the actual page as below.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_061f62f59ee100d7b7178dbc514beda7.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You\n can also add attachment to your products, set on/off shelf, and add \nCSS/JS code in the action section of the product list.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_3342c329eb86c0bd828b516179be0c78.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',66,',1,14,26,66,89,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:10:28','2016-12-27 09:55:04',76,4,'en'),(95,'Board moderator and descriptions','BM','','','<p>Usually you will have to add descriptions and board moderators for your boards, which can be done via \"Edit\" function.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Login Changer backend with your admin account. Go to <strong>User</strong>-&gt;<strong>Forum</strong>-&gt;<strong>Board</strong> and click \"<strong>Edit</strong>\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5f1399267efc36bddd5087d7b65a6955.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Select a child board and add descriptions.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_9d732d1ea5d9ece7918e0dbbc2556918.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Boards on your website will show BM and descriptions.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_013267c1a6202c9dbe494ce627e1835c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',92,',1,14,25,92,95,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:21:03','2016-12-27 11:29:22',93,2,'en'),(96,'Edit, delete, reply and stick a thread','','','','<p>Admin has to maintain a forum by \"Reply\", “Delete”, “Sticky” and \"Edit\" a post.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>If you have a new reply, you will see the icon is not others,</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_80b73e9e4062ea3090b0dfcdde360712.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>If you have a new post, you will see the green icon in front of its title. If it is sticky, you will see the Sticky tag.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5ab5b6c3b7e3a3ec1360e4b2c09ab2c1.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can reply, edit and stick a post by clicking the ACTION buttons shown in the red box. If you hid a post, only you and the one who wrote this post can see it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_9d9f3cb238db0dec40f01453cbf1f258.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',92,',1,14,25,92,96,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 13:21:03','2016-12-27 13:38:35',88,3,'en'),(77,'Blog','','','','','chapter',15,',1,14,15,77,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:21:26','2016-08-25 11:22:04',0,3,'en'),(78,'Book/Manual','','','','','chapter',15,',1,14,15,78,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:21:26','2016-08-25 11:22:04',0,4,'en'),(79,'Submission','','','','','chapter',15,',1,14,15,79,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:21:26','2016-12-26 11:04:59',0,5,'en'),(80,'Changer blog','','','','<p>It is popular to use a few words to communicate with others and post \nyour thoughts, with the rapid development of social media, such\n as Wechat, Twitter, etc. Fewer people are writing blogs now, but we \nbelieve that blog can demonstrate the value of a team and promote their \nproducts. Therefore, Changer has build-in blog to spread your thoughts \nand promotions.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>It is quite simple to manage a blog, \njust like to manage articles. You can manage categories, and blogs. \nPlease refer to Chapter <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.changercms.com/book/changermanual/publisharticles-74.html\"><em>3.1.1.2 Publish an article.</em></a></p>\n<p><em><br />\n</em></p>\n<p>Go to <strong>CMS</strong>-&gt;<strong>Blog</strong> and you can manage blogs here, which is like Manage Article.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_2f2b8e09270717d1785bb772c2a1e72b.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',77,',1,14,15,77,80,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:22:29','2016-12-23 14:01:27',98,1,'en'),(49,'Site','site','info;site;','','<p>The basic information of a site includes name of the site, date of creation, slogan, description, registration number, etc. You have to set up those information before you create a site.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Login Changer backend with your admin account.</p>\n<p>2.Click \"Settings\"-&gt; \"Site\"-&gt;\"Site settings\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_5311a4d4915ee98a83000bdd2db6af20.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Note:</p>\n<p>1. Date of creation is the date that the site is created. This information is used to generate copy right info in the footer of the frontend.</p>\n<p>2. Keyword is very important, because it is main push word. Please set keywords properly.</p>\n<p>3. Site logan describes what the site is for and it will be shown in the center of the header.</p>\n<p>4.Site descrition will show in the meta tab of the header, so it is also very important.</p>\n<p>5. Meta info have tabs like &lt;meta&gt;&lt;script&gt;&lt;style&gt;&lt;link&gt;.</p>\n<p>6. The latest version of Changer has added status, type, language, main domain, accessible domain name and function switch. It is default settings that interactive, search and mall aspects are off. You can manually switch it on if you want to.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201606/f_72fc654232770a201a760a31039f5aec.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','chapter',22,',1,14,22,49,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-24 10:38:19','2016-12-28 11:25:31',0,1,'en'),(111,'Full text retrieval','textretrieval','full;text;retrive;','','<p>You can use built-in search tool, if you installed Changer 4.2+. Full text retrieval can only be seen if it is checked\n in <strong>Set</strong>. Go to \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\" and chech Search first.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_8cd136473acba91b940a61ce6d37005c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"Full \ntext retrieval\"-&gt;\"Update Index\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_245b6d1c3b3bac15c302b2a90a46e708.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>After it is updated, you would \nsee the updated content.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_10d8d295e5ba6c18e7e76d639e05f1b3.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',49,',1,14,22,49,111,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:23:00','2016-12-28 14:53:52',128,9,'en'),(169,'Reward points','','','','<p>With Changer 4.5+, reward points feature is \navailable. You can use \npoints as a set of value measurement and the warm-up for events.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Go to \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Basic settings\". Check \"Points\" function.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_e1171fa0910b4e4690d31acf7dadae4f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2.\n Go to \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Points\" and add rules to define how many points \nusers can get by certain action. For example, user can earn 2 points by login. There is default settings of points and you can it later. If not changed, default rules will be executed.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. After setting rules, members can view their reward points in&nbsp; User-&gt;\"Points\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_4516810881fb8120ad6ab538ad3dea22.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',164,',1,14,22,164,169,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-12-28 14:40:32','2016-12-28 15:23:33',52,1,'en'),(118,'Theme','','','','<p>Changer has four build-in template, including Default, Changer Tartan, Clean and Wide. You can swtich them at the backend. You can use a blank one to design your own template.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to UI-&gt;UI-&gt;Theme.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_fbde50615cba18405ee51e79a7d87e12.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Except built-in themes, more can be downloaded from the Theme Store. You can click those labels to view different templates, free and paid templates.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_ca700f1ccc73e57088c2f23ee5c6f9ec.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can also uploade template you coded.</p>\n<br />\n<p><strong>Upload your template</strong></p>\n<p>Go to <strong>UI</strong>, you will see \"Import\" ans \"Export\" at the upper right of the page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_1b89368ca3c0df4fe09bcb091e43f399.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<ul><li>You have to use Changer code template and ZentaoPHP to code your template. Do NOT upload thrid party template. <strong>ZentaoPHP</strong> can be found here&nbsp;<a href=\"http://devel.cnezsoft.com/book/zentaophphelp.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://devel.cnezsoft.com/book/zentaophphelp.html </a>and <strong>Changer source code</strong> can be downloaded here <a href=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/download.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chanzhi.org/download.html</a><br />\n</li>\n<li>Copy your template code file to Changer source code directory.&nbsp; The template directory should look like what is in the screenshot below.&nbsp; <em>db</em> and <em>system</em> should not be modified, <em>doc</em> and <em>www</em> is what you have to modify. You have to code yaml in doc. <em>www</em> is file for style.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201510/f_6756078eb4265e8dd289fc3796d66821.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<ul><li>Create a .zip file and click \"Import\".<br />\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can also edit your template online via Visual Editor and related developement documents. Third part designers and website building agencies are welcome to develop templates.</p>\n<br />','article',61,',1,14,23,61,118,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 09:30:23','2016-12-27 15:02:38',115,1,'en'),(119,'Layout','layout','layout','','<p>Go to \"UI\"-&gt;\"UI\"-&gt;\"Layout\", you can see contents that you can maintain on one page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_bb5ef819a71e059f4bd372d007e82aaa.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Let\'s say you want to put \"About Us\", \"Latest\" and \"Contact Us\" in the middle of your Home page. Click \"Homepage\"-&gt;\"Middle\", a window will pop out.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_fe67dc5fe325adc30230bf5fe46e3e27.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Set the width and other attributions, and click \"Save\" to finish layout settings.</p>','article',61,',1,14,23,61,119,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 09:30:23','2016-12-27 15:18:46',108,2,'en'),(120,'Appearance','ui','UI','','<p>Go to \"UI\"-&gt;\"UI\"-&gt;\"Appearance\". You can customize appearence. There are items you need to customize, if you choose default theme, such as basic style, navigation, widget, button etc.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_f50df75384ed35bc6f8663ed37910140.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"Desktop\" to switch between Destop mode and Mobile mode. You have to set mobile mode on by going to \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Basic settings\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_fbbf3180dadfd66bd48fe6ffed0be715.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',61,',1,14,23,61,120,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 09:30:23','2016-12-27 16:08:47',112,3,'en'),(121,'Code','code','code','','<p>Go to \"UI\"-&gt;\"UI\"-&gt;\"Code\" to add CSS/ JS code to customize your website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_06463bee6c367e9a91a05112833cb15d.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',61,',1,14,23,61,121,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 09:30:23','2016-12-27 16:15:12',102,4,'en'),(122,'Source','material','material','','<p>Source library has been add to Changer. You can upload images and retrieve them when you want to use images. Please note:</p>\n<p>1. Each template in source library is separate and independent.</p>\n<p>2. Click \"Upload\" to add your images to the library.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_cabd04e2a31c55f195698c27c5798269.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',61,',1,14,23,61,122,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 09:30:00','2016-12-27 16:31:12',111,5,'en'),(123,'Mobile site','mobile','mobie','','<p>Changer has separate mobile site which can save data for mobile users.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Site settings\". Switch on \"Mobile Site\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_69b04d56e6f90e766a37de13f99557df.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to UI-&gt; Mobile to set customized template, logo, icon, slide, widget, layout, and source etc.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_e185bebc1c1e630158cd416be5f2cb9b.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>1. If you don\'t do any mobile settings, a web-based responsive layout will show when using a mobile to visit your site.</p>\n<p>2. If you have set mobile interface and layout and you want to restore it to web responsive layout, you have to login your databse and delete section=\'template\' and `key` = \'mobile\' in eps_config sheet. (If you installed Changer 4.4.1 +,&nbsp; go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Baisc settings\" to switch it off.)</p>\n<p>3. For detailed mobile interface settings, please refer to Chapter <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://changercms.com/book/changermanual/layout-119.html\"><em>2.5.1.2 Layout</em></a></p>','article',61,',1,14,23,61,123,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 09:51:36','2016-12-27 16:45:42',116,6,'en'),(114,'System Maintainence','','','','','chapter',1,',1,114,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:31:23','2016-08-25 15:32:09',0,4,'en'),(115,'Changer Customization','','','','','chapter',1,',1,115,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:31:23','2016-08-29 10:12:22',0,5,'en'),(116,'Zsite','','','','','chapter',1,',1,116,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:31:23','2016-08-25 15:32:09',0,6,'en'),(117,'Sensitive words and attachment','terms-attach','sensitiveterms;attachment','','<p><strong>Sensitive words settings</strong></p>\n<p>The default settings of sensitive words filter is off. Go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Security\"-&gt;\"Sensitive&nbsp;words filter\" to switch it on/off.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201608/f_51933c883661947ac023fd8fe0b54a1a.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Once it is on, you can see default sensitive words. You can add sensitive words and separate them with commas.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201608/f_80528532b25ad9d4b88f9c6ded8cd8c2.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>Once it is on, any content contains sensitive words cannot be publish on your website, and a notice will let you know what contains sensitive words.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Attachment</strong></p>\n<p>Go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Security\"-&gt;\"Attachment\", Check the box \"whether attachment is alllowed to upload\". If you check the box, you can set up file formats that can be uploaded.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201608/f_0368000f9ccc457270e29ee21e2bd113.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:1px solid #E5E5E5;\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',67,',1,14,22,67,117,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:32:54','2016-12-28 11:29:15',120,3,'en'),(61,'Interface','','','','','chapter',23,',1,14,23,61,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-24 17:08:09','2016-08-26 14:52:56',0,1,'en'),(62,'Logo','','','','','chapter',23,',1,14,23,62,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-24 17:08:09','2016-08-26 14:52:56',0,2,'en'),(63,'Widget','block','','','','chapter',23,',1,14,23,63,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-24 17:08:09','2016-12-27 14:39:56',0,5,'en'),(65,'Orders and Settings','orders','','','<p>You have to check Mall feature in Set-&gt;Site-&gt;Basic setttings before use it. With Mall module, you can check and manae your orders, manage your products and do order related settings. Please refer to the Chapter <em>3.2.2 </em><em>Prodcut </em>to manage your products.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>The following will show you the order related settings.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Manage your orders</strong></p>\n<p>Go to \"Mall\"-&gt;\"Order\", you can see all the orders here.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5c4a55fd87595633220fe7b64fbb5d35.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Ship</strong> and choose delivery service, tracking number, etc.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_765b35c42fd4e45bb8e04c40739921f2.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Shipping company can be added by going to \"<strong>Mall</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Settings</strong>\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_44bc4e4a76df444102e792421cb1b179.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Other settings</strong></p>\n<p>You set recieving cycel and transaction type. Alipay is supported in Changer Mall. You can configure it in Alipay.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_d29304492aff3809cd94f9d1de33459f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',26,',1,14,26,65,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:36:40','2016-12-26 14:19:52',87,1,'en'),(66,'Product','','','','','chapter',26,',1,14,26,66,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:36:40','2016-08-25 11:30:26',0,2,'en'),(67,'Security','security','security','','','chapter',22,',1,14,22,67,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:41:52','2016-12-28 11:25:31',0,5,'en'),(69,'Basic settings','','basicsettings','','<p>Changer 4.3 Beta+ has security settings. You can do basic security settings, attachement settings and sensitive term settings. Let\'s see how basic security settings are done.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"<strong>Set</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Security</strong>\", you can set</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_a974939cc10521fd6eb31f9fca6956bf.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<ul><li>security code verification</li>\n<li>verification for key actions<br />\n</li>\n<li>whether login is required to view your website</li>\n<li>whether verification is required when Admin logs in</li>\n<li>whether check IP address when one logs in backend</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Attachment Upload</strong> include,</p>\n<ul><li>whether members can upload attachment to your website</li>\n<li>which format can be uploaded to your website</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_9958d549a06efc17ad413b49d3aecd5c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Sensitive Words</strong> setting means whether sensitive words will be detected and filtered.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_7627ec67fea25b5dc6a5e7f6d0078e60.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',67,',1,14,22,67,69,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:44:51','2016-12-29 10:22:42',138,1,'en'),(70,'Filter and Blacklist/Whitelist settings','filtersettings','filtersettings','','<p>Changer 4.6+ has anti-malware feature now. You can do those settings at the backend, including filters, blacklists and whitelists. It will help you fight against malware and spam.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Filter settings</p>\n<p>IP and account filters. You can set limits to certain operations of an IP/account, such as \"Login failed\", \"registration\", \"password retrieval\", \"password reset failed\", \"publish a topic\", \"write a comment\", \"reply a post\", \"POST requests\", \"search\", \"404 error\", \"verification code error\", etc. The screenshot shows the default settings, and you can alwasy adjust it according to your actual requirements.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_d0e4bb2c0c0597c881bce0a336d61923.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Blacklist</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You can add an IP address, account, keyword, webstie, email address to your blacklist. Clich \"Add to blacklist\" at the upper right of the page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5d2ce8bddbd83567ce5450727b26f065.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>A window will pop out. Add IP/account/keywords and the reason, click \"Save\" to block it. Once added, it cannot publish any content to your website. The default removal time is in 5 minutes.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_cce2cdcecbaa50a229800fbf246e55cc.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. Whitelist</p>\n<p>IP/account added to whitelist will not be blocked by filter/blacklist. If you want to add more to the whitelist, use comma to seperate them. You have to use your addmin password to add it to whitelist.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_1535d8cf4a3c821e7de7caf981e0c29a.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',67,',1,14,22,67,70,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:44:51','2016-12-29 10:53:55',121,2,'en'),(71,'Security questions','securitycode','securitycode;verification','','<p>Changer 5.0 or higher has verification code settings.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Login backend, go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Security\"-&gt;\"basic settings\"-&gt;\"frontend list\". You can choose \"Always\", \"once sensitive words detected\", or \"Never\" use verification code.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_7d7739fd58a55d361002bcea80e4d914.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>If you choose \"Always\", go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Security\"-&gt;\"verification code settings\" to add your verification questions and answers. You can detele or add more Q&amp;As.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_ed85c5a19ea8e60432cb9f54d012a848.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>At the frontend, verification questions will be shuffled and one of them will show randomly. Only the correct answer can get members through and then they can pulish content on your website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201512/f_60005b945dd72a3db52afaf0bf31120f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',67,',1,14,22,67,71,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:44:51','2016-12-28 11:29:15',114,4,'en'),(72,'Administrators settings','adminsettings','adminsettings','','<p>In security settings, you can manage admin account, privileges, and login log.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Security\"-&gt;\"Administrator\", you eill see the list of administrators. You can manage the list by editing the inforamtion of admins, add/delete/disable an admin.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_ea49a18f392463312f4893285605e9ce.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Create a admin group.</p>\n<p>Click \"Add a group\" , and name your group and describe it briefly. Click \"Save\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_f5c9f09bb60c9096ce799a22ec5f5f5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Once the group is created, you can use \"Privilege\" to manage each admin\'s privileges, \"Member\" to add admins to the group and \"Edit\"/\"Delete\" them.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_d1e75edeebfffdf2ff34f80572aa9323.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"Privilege\", and you will see the page to set privileges. Check privileges you want to add to the admin, then the admin will have the checked privileges.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_08d5ac7e35c2f11564e0fb9c95a6e1e1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"Member\", check the admin you want to add to the group. Once \"Save\"d, that admin will have the same privileges as the rest of the group.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_1c82ea577943805ecb3ea9aa318ff5c2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>In \"Login log\", it records details of each admin\'s operation. If anything abnormal, you can disable/modify that admin password.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_54b5a087d85d60d473d4734f12b10cb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',67,',1,14,22,67,72,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 09:44:51','2016-12-28 11:29:15',117,5,'en'),(73,'Article Category','articlecategory','category;article','','<p>Article content management is a must-have function for a website \nbuilder, so Changer has built in such function. Before adding any content to your\n website, let us add categories of articles first.</p>\n<h4>1. Login backend</h4>\n<p>Login Changer with admin account, such as http://192.168.1.99/admin.php.</p>\n<h4>2. Manage categories</h4>\n<p>Click <strong>CMS</strong>-&gt;<strong>Article</strong><strong></strong>, and all articles will show at the right column.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_dc0894fcb2c56384369611384ff91c2d.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Manage Category </strong>and you can set names, alias, and child categories.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_cb90c3e071947635b32dd8222aa868c1.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Category can have alias(no hyphens) so to do SEO.<br />\n</li>\n<li>Five categories can be added at the one time. If you want to add more \nthan five categories, save the first five and add the rest of them.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3. Maintain a child category<br />\n</h4>\n<p>You\n can add as many child categories as you like. Choose a category, click <strong>Child</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_195529dbed751eb244cf288617763b1f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',30,',1,14,15,30,73,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:14:30','2016-12-23 10:11:22',76,1,'en'),(74,'Publish an Article','publisharticles','','','<p>After you add categories, you can start to add articles.</p>\n<p>1. Login Changer as admin. Go to <strong>CMS</strong>-&gt;<strong>Article</strong>, and click <strong>Add Article</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_6bd6fe82f1d057c1efe5230f5b922288.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>1. When publishing an article, you must choose a category. You can choose multiply categories.</p>\n<p>2. You can set up the source of the articel, like whether it is original or not. If not, you can add the URL.</p>\n<p>3. Alias, keywords and abstract are for SEO, so you can use them to advance SEO.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_c49a7e67c83604f2ca54aee7964e38f6.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',30,',1,14,15,30,74,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:16:10','2016-12-23 10:42:27',79,2,'en'),(76,'Changer page makes website building flexible','','','','<p>The difference between a page and an article is that a page does not \nbelong to any category. It is usually used to keep information such as \n\"Contact Us\", \"Company Information\" etc.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Login the Changer with your admin account. Go to <strong>CMS</strong> and Click <strong>Page</strong> , you will see where you \ncan manage page, which is quite similar to edit an article.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_1ade8ec311d662274de904ac391a5b53.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',32,',1,14,15,32,76,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 11:20:04','2016-12-23 13:44:18',96,1,'en'),(98,'User list','userlist','','','<p>Check <strong>User</strong> at <strong>Set</strong>-&gt;<strong>Site</strong>-&gt;<strong>Basic settings</strong> to switch on user related features, such as <strong>Comment</strong> and <strong>Forum</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5908cea20b0dfecb7805eb7a862d04a0.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to <strong>User </strong>and you will see the user list.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5249068101c5a1574603b884737da8ad.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. You can check members in this list, or search members by their IDs.</p>\n<p>2. Choose a member to edit. You can set one admin and reset password if one forgot the password.</p>\n<p>3. You can disable certain member account.</p>\n<p>4. Click <strong>Add a User</strong> and you will see a page as shown below to verify.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_bbd0b9317418465e738369a23ba2d079.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Follow the instructions to verify your action and then enter</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_cc5b2b2e6b991f200fc7a3c75468e3cc.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>All comments/messages can be viewed only if they have been \nreviewed and published by the admin. Admin can go to \n\"User\"-&gt;\"Message\" to review, reply, or delete messages.</p>\n<p>If Board module is switched on, you can also see topics and the replies here, and you can also edit, delete, and hide those here.</p>\n<p>If Submission module is on, contributions can be checked and reviewed here.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_b0d07f0664af873cedb594bebab508f1.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',90,',1,14,25,90,98,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 14:21:58','2016-12-27 10:20:58',84,1,'en'),(99,'Traffic Statistics','trafficstatistics','trafficstatistics','','<p>Changer 4.5+ has traffic statistics function. You can view your reports such as statistics about search engines, keywords, domains, customer, page views, etc. You can know the situation of your website operation and maintenance without adding third party statistic code yourself.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Site settings\", check \"Statistics\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_1cf8c5e7d46c5cd36933dd51fd9bedac.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"SEO\"-&gt;\"Stats\", then you will see traffic statistics.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_3d116dd0e86d483cbc04ee9155421637.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can also set how long you want the statistics to be saved.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_58764abdf766e06e39cea66a0346d2a5.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',29,',1,14,29,99,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 14:39:09','2016-12-27 14:08:08',79,1,'en'),(100,'Keywords','keywords','keywords','','<p>You can set keywords in every module in Changer. In order to better manage those keywords, Keywords can be set in SEO module.</p>\n<p>You can see how many keywords and their weight.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can set links to each keyword. When certain keyword is shown on your website, it will be replaced with corresponding links.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_239c2b36cd40274d4b644503765384f3.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>1. Weight is how many times a keyword has been used.</p>\n<p>2. Click \"Link\" to edit the links that this keyword is related.</p>','article',29,',1,14,29,100,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 14:39:09','2016-12-27 14:31:03',85,2,'en'),(101,'Links','links','links','','<p>Links is a must-have function for a website. In Changer, it is very easy to set links. Go to \"SEO\"-&gt;\"Links\". You will see a page for you to edit links</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_6c50ee7702c9a6a085fb43cf08fc4ddf.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>There are two kinds of links,</p>\n<ul><li>Homepage Links that will show links on homepage</li>\n<li>Links will be shown on other pages.<br />\n</li>\n</ul>','article',29,',1,14,29,101,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 14:39:09','2016-12-27 14:34:50',86,3,'en'),(102,'Domain settings','','','','<div class=\"textarea-wrap\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://fanyi.baidu.com/translate###\" class=\"operate-btn op-sound data-hover-tip\"> </a> <div class=\"output-bd\"><p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\">Domain settings can set the main domain name and domain name allowed, as well as the default access protocol. Usually, you don\'t have to change anything. Just use the default settings. However, if\n you have more than one domain name to jump to the same site, the main \ndomain name can be the one you want to display after the jump, the </span><span class=\"\">prerequisite of which is that you have to resolve the domain name.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\"><br />\n</span> </p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\">If you want to switch the default access protocol, the prerequisite is to do HTTPS certificate application.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\"><br />\n</span> </p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\">Click the question mark at the end of domain names for more information.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\"><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_31740436c82b4548b4bc9d149dc33878.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\"><br />\n</span> </p>\n</div>','article',49,',1,14,22,49,102,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:18:32','2016-12-28 13:41:08',140,2,'en'),(103,'CND settings','cndsettings','CND;settings','','<p>Go to \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"CND settings\", and you will see the setting page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_c72d2a086face27faa2493e6798f0d95.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',49,',1,14,22,49,103,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:18:32','2016-12-28 13:41:08',124,3,'en'),(104,'Cache settings','cachesettings','cache;settings','','<p>Changer has cache settings, if you installed its version 5.3+. It can help accelerate your website loading. You can \nsimply switch it on/off by one click.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Cache settings\". You will see the page below.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_540b45ead79a10fac57bdce72e27090c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',49,',1,14,22,49,104,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:18:32','2016-12-28 13:45:38',124,4,'en'),(105,'Homepage menu','homepagesettings','homepage;menu;settings','','<p>Admin can customize the homepage navigation and add features that often used on homepage menu, so it will\n be convenient to guide your website.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"Set\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Homepage menu\". You can check features that you want to add to it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_577c705f848137fd2e98525da927aaab.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Check those your want to add, and you will see them on the homepage of Changer backend once login.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_e4f18498dd7bff238c8da96fe6dfa55c.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',49,',1,14,22,49,105,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:18:32','2016-12-28 13:50:29',123,5,'en'),(113,'Backup/Restore','restorebackup','backup;restore','','<p>With Changer 5.3+, you can restore your backup, which means \nyou can restore the backup of website database, attachments, CSS styles \nand such content that your users added.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Backup files will be \nstored in <em>YOUR CHANGER DIRECTORY</em>\\system\\tmp\\backup, which include a \ndata file, a doc file and a template file. Those files are all .php file\n for securities.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_6f70f2bd9d1f246e36e8b5014ce39d38.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',49,',1,14,22,49,113,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-25 15:24:52','2016-12-28 14:01:31',122,6,'en'),(124,'Slides','slides','slides','','<p>A nice slides on your homepage can be eye catching. Use Changer to create slides. With Changer 4.3 Beta+, Slide has been built-in, which means you can create multiply groups of slides and distribute them to several pages.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Go to \"<strong>UI</strong>\"-&gt;\"<strong>Slide</strong>\". Click \"Create a group\" to start upload your slides.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_b356f81fc55c72dd6519aeda30dae2d5.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>1. If you \"Create a group\" and upload slide to the default template, it will also show in Changer Tartan and Wide-screen themes.</p>\n<p>2. If you add \"Slide\" and its layout in default template settings, it will only show in default template. If you change the template to Changer Tartan or wide-screen, you have to add \"Slide\" and its layout again.</p>\n<p>3. The size of images you uploaded to be in the same group should be the same.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. After you upload images to create sildes, you can upload an image or set certain color as its background. If you check \"Global\", the button will show on every slide. With Changer 4.3 Beta+, you can choose images from source library.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_7d51c1930c9b6bba5c31b5183c554ab3.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>3. You can upload several slides to one group, and switch their orders by clicking arrows next to the slide.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_3da52b27c315406253397c6507582439.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',23,',1,14,23,124,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 14:50:37','2016-12-28 09:06:34',113,3,'en'),(125,'Navigation','navagation','navigation','','<p>Now it comes to set navigations after setting basic information and logos. Changer has four types of naviagation, system module, product category, article category, blog category, page and custom. System module includes Homepage, About Us, Contact Us, Forum, Blog, Book and Message. Custom means you can set the title and the link of a navigation bar.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"UI\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Navigation\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_7590c8edb0ecd31cbb12c03e5cbb4d90.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Select a system module and enter the title for it which does not have to be the same as the module name.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_32c83cd325b715cdbbc79852ec1952c8.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\nYou can also add a child by clicking the last but second button and change the order by clicking the last button.<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_92e9b3ba36857ff69c2c139e58ac9251.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p>1. Each title of a navigation can be modified.</p>\n<p>2. You can set to open a navigation in a new/current window.</p>\n<p>3. Use the cross at the end of each navigation settings to change the order.</p>','article',23,',1,14,23,125,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 14:50:37','2016-12-28 09:21:56',106,4,'en'),(126,'Visual Editor','','','','<p>From Changer 4.5, visual editor has been integrated. Visual editor can give you an intuitive editing.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to <strong>UI</strong> and click<strong> Visual Editor</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_590e144987390ab1432f0b402f62846b.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Website will be open in Edit mode. Hover the block you want to edit, a group of buttons, such as Edit, Delete, will appear.&nbsp; Click a button, a corresponding pop-out window will show.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_c948e3cf5efc2b75083d6ae87c9b8b77.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click \"All Pages/Header\", \"Homepage/Header\", \"Homepage/Middle\", \"Homepage/Bottom\" to add a new widget. Or simply click \"Add\".</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_c7028c5d71a7c7263ecefc45c54c0c1f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can also change the name and logo for your website by Visual Editor.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_1061fdf1a43ec6bb5582ec8a4dac8630.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can remove a widget and change its layout.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_f642ab81d8411fdcf200fe4c8e31e1ea.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',23,',1,14,23,126,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 14:50:37','2016-12-28 10:28:26',108,6,'en'),(127,'Settings','','','','<p>In <strong>UI</strong>-&gt;<strong>Settings</strong>, you can set product visit count, QR code and etc. You can also set the number of lists for Article, Product, Blog, Message, Board and Reply. You can also set the size of a thumbnail for customized images.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_8510eff1819b63472c72827bf3d8c619.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Once you switch on the operating information, it will show on your website,</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_91a5e6c3284851d4ce6c6a378a5b28d3.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',23,',1,14,23,127,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 14:50:37','2016-12-28 11:11:03',114,7,'en'),(128,'Custom','','','','<p>From Changer 5.3+,<strong> Custom</strong> is added. You can edit all template on code level in Changer, which is very convenient.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to <strong>UI</strong>-&gt;<strong>Custom</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_9bf9d3c86ea81741c0ae8e014c148d4a.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',23,',1,14,23,128,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 14:50:37','2016-12-28 11:21:13',118,8,'en'),(129,'Site logo','sitelogo','','site logo','<p>A logo is a very important part of your corporate image (CI). A right logo can impress your customers, so we suggest you hired a professional designer. Now let\'s see how to set logos in Changer.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"UI\"-&gt;\"Logo\". Click \"Upload a logo\" and choose the log picture you want to upload.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_5de8a11d61b83d4b3d6f87d2c48ffc33.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',62,',1,14,23,62,129,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 15:00:00','2016-12-27 16:51:29',115,1,'en'),(130,'Site favicon','setfavicon','setfavicon','','<h4>1. What is favicon?</h4>\n<p>Favicon is an abbreviation of favorites icon, as known as webste icon/page icon/urlicon. Favicon is an icon that relates to a website or a web page. Favicon.ico is usually used as thumbnail of website logo, which will show in a browser\'s address bar or a tag. All major browsers support favicons.</p>\n<h4>2. Upload a favicon to Changer</h4>\n<p>Go to \"UI\"-&gt;\"Interface\"-&gt;\"Logo\". Click \"Upload favicon\" to upload. Please note that the favicon has to be.ico file.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_90c9b5194c35cd1c62319bfc676da4e2.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h4>3. .ico converter</h4>\n<p>A lot .ico converters are available online. Upload a picture and it will generate an image in .ico format for you. Here are some favicon converters</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.bitbug.net/\">http://www.bitbug.net/</a> </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.ico.la/\">http://www.ico.la/</a> </p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',62,',1,14,23,62,130,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 15:03:26','2016-12-27 16:53:08',101,2,'en'),(131,'Manage a widget','module','module','','<p>Web page layout is several widgets put together. You have to add widgets before you customize layout for your site. In Changer, you can add, edit, or delete a widget.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"UI\"-&gt;\"Widget\". and click \"Add\" in \"Custom\" to add a customized widget.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_fd4f2b7e313a7efc88f7e16d5357cd11.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Changer&nbsp;4.3 Beta+ has 19 types of widgets available. You can set values for each widget. Take \"Latest Article\" for example, the values include the number of new articles and the number shown in that widget.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_9f7ba0c6d8d3d2ae484f81b5c07919c1.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',63,',1,14,23,63,131,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 16:30:54','2016-12-28 09:40:26',123,1,'en'),(132,'Example: customized widget','blockcode','module;code','','<p>Here we will give an example of how to use a widget and its features to deploy code to do statistic reports.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. Go to<strong> UI</strong>-&gt;<strong>Widget</strong>-&gt;<strong>Custom Widget</strong> and click <strong>Add</strong> to copy code to it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_e5981eccb87b63757088de524437911f.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Save </strong>and this widget will show in custom widget.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_b34b5db75aafe6373062597622e9f957.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. Go to<strong> UI</strong>-&gt;<strong>UI</strong>-&gt;<strong>Layout</strong> and add this custom widget to the footer of each page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_d43f0babd783df573ec1514278992653.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Select this custom widget from the drop-down list and you will see the code on footer of all pages.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_73ac4874112e5ab1582284c922f0cd6b.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',63,',1,14,23,63,132,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-26 16:30:54','2016-12-28 09:59:29',131,2,'en'),(167,'Contact','','','','<p>Click \"Set\"-&gt;\"Company\"-&gt;\"Contact\" to add your contact information.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_8166454ceb85d9637198bc3fbfe34b99.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',163,',1,14,22,163,167,',5,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-12-28 11:27:27','2016-12-28 14:05:15',58,2,'en'),(134,'Ext','','','','','chapter',14,',1,14,134,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-29 08:57:50','2016-12-28 14:17:25',0,6,'en'),(135,'Extensions and Themes','plugins','extension;template','','<p>Go to \"Ext\" at Changer, you will see \"Extensions\" and \"Template\". You can manange extensions here. There are three types of extensions, Installed, Deactivated and Available.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_9a3600d6b3fe2900bcd7c707382135f6.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can install Changer extensions locally. Click \"Get Extensions\" at the upper right of the window. Changer official extensions and third party ones will show. You can install extensions by one click and it will automatically run and install. If automatic installation is not working, download it to your machine first and then instal it manually.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can also view Changer themes by going to \"Ext\"-&gt;\"Themes\" and check the theme details and shop it online.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',134,',1,14,134,135,',4,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-29 08:58:35','2016-12-28 14:17:04',78,1,'en'),(136,'Configure web server for URL access','staticaccess','URLaccess','','<p>Changer support two kinds of access, one is traditional \"get\" , such as /?m=article&amp;id=123 (123 is the name of the article you want to view), and the other one is to use URL, such as /article-view-123.html.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Changer has built-in URL path which is search engine friendly. The URL address mentioned above will be article/123.html. if the article 12 belongs to certain category which has an alias, say news, the address will be news/123.html.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>First, you have to configure webserver for URL access. If you use site hosting, URL access is usually switched on. If not, please follow the instructions below to configure your web server.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Apache:</strong> </p>\n<p>1. Configure apache and load <span style=\"color:#006600;\"><strong>mod_rewrite</strong></span>.</p>\n<p>2. Configure .htaccess in the directory of chanzhieps/www. For exmaple,</p>\n<p>&lt;Directory /home/chanzhieps/www&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Options FollowSymLinks Indexes<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#006600;\"><strong>AllowOverride All</strong></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/Directory&gt;</p>\n<p><strong><br />\n</strong> </p>\n<p><strong>nginx:</strong> </p>\n<p>location / <br />\n{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#006600;\"><strong> try_files $uri $uri/ /index.php?$args;</strong></span><br />\n}<br />\n<br />\nlocation ~ \\.php$ <br />\n{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fastcgi_pass&nbsp; unix:/var/run/php5-fpm.sock;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fastcgi_index index.php;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#006600;\"><strong>fastcgi_param PATH_INFO $request_uri;</strong></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; include modules-enabled/fastcgi.conf;<br />\n}</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>If you have already installed Changer and would like to use URL access, please make sure the configuration above is done first, and then reinstall Changer, or modify requestType to PATH_INFO in chanzhi/system/config/my.php (5.2+ version has to choose Path_Info by going to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Site\"-&gt;\"Basic settings\"-&gt;\"Request Type”).</p>','article',114,',1,114,136,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-29 09:14:37','2016-12-29 10:55:50',74,1,'en'),(137,'Backup Changer','backupChanger','backup','','<p>Admin should backup Changer regularly. There are two types of data in Changer that need to back up, database and attachment.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>For database backup, use phpmyadmin, mysqldump, or backup provided at your web server.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>For attachement, backup attachement in the directory of www/data/upload.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div class=\"trans-left\"><div class=\"trans-input-wrap\"><div class=\"input-wrap\"><div class=\"textarea-wrap\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://fanyi.baidu.com/translate###\" class=\"operate-btn op-sound data-hover-tip\"> </a> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"output-bd\"><p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\">Changer 5.3+&nbsp; has a template editing function, which is saved in the system/tmp/template directory If you modify the \ntemplate, you need to backup the directory.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\"><br />\n</span> </p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\">Changer 5.3+ has backup restore \nfunction. Go to <strong>Set</strong> -&gt; <strong>Site</strong> -&gt; <strong>Backup/Restore</strong>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ordinary-output target-output clearfix\"><span class=\"\"><img src=\"/data/upload/201612/f_f07bcd3ae77a7324a1fe0ba77f0ecacd.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> </p>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',114,',1,114,137,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-29 09:14:37','2016-12-29 10:57:58',73,2,'en'),(138,'Before you start','changerframework','framework','','<p>Changer use ZentaoPHP as its framework and ZUI as its frontend framework, and both of the frameworks are developed by out team. Therefore, you will have to know ZentaoPHP and ZUI before you customize your website.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Please note:</p>\n<p>Changer is develop based on ZPL (Z Public License). <span style=\"color:#E53333;\">Any modification to Changer logs, including logs at the right bottow of the frontend and backend, and the logo at the login ingterface of the</span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"> backend, is <strong>NOT</strong> allowed.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p>1. ZentaoPHP Manual：<a href=\"http://devel.cnezsoft.com/book/zentaophphelp.html\">http://devel.cnezsoft.com/book/zentaophphelp.html</a></p>\n<p>2. ZentaoPHP Customization Manual：<a href=\"http://devel.cnezsoft.com/book/extension.html\">http://devel.cnezsoft.com/book/extension.html</a></p>\n<p>3. ZUI html5 Manual：<a href=\"http://www.zui.sexy\">http://www.zui.sexy</a></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',115,',1,115,138,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-29 10:12:30','2016-11-01 14:03:38',66,1,'en'),(139,'Changer source code','changersourcecode','sourcecode','','<p>Changer source code can be reached at</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Github: <a href=\"https://github.com/easysoft/chanzhieps/\">https://github.com/easysoft/chanzhieps/</a></p>\n<p>oschina: <a href=\"http://git.oschina.net/wwccss/chanzhieps\">http://git.oschina.net/wwccss/chanzhieps</a></p>\n<p>csdn:<a href=\"https://code.csdn.net/wang_chun_sheng/chanzhieps\"> https://code.csdn.net/wang_chun_sheng/chanzhieps</a></p>','article',115,',1,115,139,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-29 10:12:30','2016-11-01 14:04:00',69,2,'en'),(140,'Changer directory structure','changerdirectory','directory','','<p>|--system&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Changer system file. Can be put in the directory of www</p>\n<p>| &nbsp; |--bin&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; executable files, scripts, such as calls by command lines</p>\n<p>| &nbsp; |--config&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; system configuration files</p>\n<p>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--config.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; default global configuration files. Can be overrode by other variables haveing the same name</p>\n<p>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--admin.php admin&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; user permission configuration</p>\n<p>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--cache.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; cache configuration</p>\n<p>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--domain.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; top level domains configuration</p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--front.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; configuration of visitors and members permissions at the frontend<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--guarder.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; access configuration<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--<span><span>menu.php</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; backend menu configuration<br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--router<span><span>.php</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SEO configuration<br />\n</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--shop<span><span>.php</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Alipay configuration</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |-<span style=\"color:#E53333;\">-</span></span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">my.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">database connection configuration and install and debug configuration</span></span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; |--db&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SQL fils for installation and update<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--</span><span></span>chanzhi.sql&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; instal php<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--upgrade1.0.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; sql</span> 1.0 upgrade <br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; |--doc&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; documents, such as modification records, licesne release etc.<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; |--framework&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ZentaoPHP and MVC <span>framework</span><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--</span>control.class.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; request processing<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--helper.class.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; tools<br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span></span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--model.class.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; data layer operation<br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span></span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--router.class.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; data forwarding<br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span></span><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--</span><span></span>seo.class.php&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SEO<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; |--</span>lib&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; lib tools, including third party lib。</p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--dao&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; database operation, SQL shield。</span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--filter&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; data filtering, format checkup, batch calls in DAO, such as check, batchcheck, autocheck</span></p>\n<p><span>| &nbsp; | &nbsp; |--front&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;