mply with relavant local laws and regulations and that of China, when using Zsite service. &nbsp;</p>\n<p>Do not use your site for any illegal activities; comply with all the rules, procedures and conventions related the use of your site.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>6.3 Zsite account should take the responsibility of the accuracy, reliability, validity and applicability of the data.</p>\n<h4>7.Rights and obligations of Zsite</h4>\n<p>7.1 Zsite should do its best to ensure normal access to the service and backup of the data.</p>\n<p>7.2 Zsite should provide consulting and technical support to paid service accounts.</p>\n<p>7.3 Service interruptions, blocked links or other defects caused by vis major, including but not limited to natural disasters, social issues, and any factors affecting the normal operation of the networks, such as system crash, data loss, hacker attacks, the impact of the telecommunications carriers’ technical adjustments and temporary closure due to government regulations, Zsite should not take any of these responsibility, but will try to reduce the loss and impact caused to Zsite accounts. &nbsp;</p>\n<p>7.4 Zsite should not take any legal responsibility for the loss caused by using the Zsite service. Zsite is not not responsible for the legal liability due to any direct, indirect, occasional, or special punitive damages and any other damages caused by the use of the web site service under any circumstances.</p>\n<p>7.5 Qingdao Xirang is not responsible for any abnormal service interruption by using Zsite, nor does it bear any losses or collateral damage.</p>\n<h4>8.Privacy and confidentiality</h4>\n<p>8.1 Personal information you fill in when you sign up for Zsite should only be used by Qingdao Xirang to contact you. Qingdao Xirang should not use it for any commercial purposes.</p>\n<p>8.2 Any data generated on Zsite by you belongs to you. Unless you take the initiative to ask us to help you troubleshoot problems, all Qingdao Xirang staff have no right to view, edit, copy, or delete your data.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h4>9. Ultimate interpretation rights</h4>\n<p>Qingdao Xirang reserves all the rights to interpret all activities, restrictions and other related terms related to Zsite..</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',116,',1,116,143,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-30 09:26:39','2016-11-02 08:21:40',71,1,'en'),(144,'Zsite versions','versions','version','','<p><table class=\"table table-list table-bordered text-center\"><tbody><tr class=\"text-center\"><th align=\"center\">version</th>\n<th>Price<br />\n</th>\n<th>Space</th>\n<th>Flow<br />\n</th>\n<th>Function</th>\n</tr>\n<tr><td>Mini</td>\n<td><br />\n</td>\n<td>200M</td>\n<td>20G/month</td>\n<td>Changer open source<br />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td>Advanced<br />\n</td>\n<td><strong></strong><br />\n</td>\n<td>500M</td>\n<td>30G/month</td>\n<td>Changer open source + charged service<br />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td>Business<br />\n</td>\n<td><strong></strong><br />\n</td>\n<td>1000M</td>\n<td>50G/month</td>\n<td><p>Changer open source + charged service</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\nNote:</p>\n<p>1. Zsite cloud service is based on Changer open source version. FTP is not provided.</p>\n<p>2. Zsite site server is in Hongkong, so no registration is required.</p>','article',116,',1,116,144,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-30 09:26:39','2016-11-02 09:08:27',71,2,'en'),(145,'Resolve domain name to Zsite server','domainresolution','domain;resolve','','<p>You need to resolve your domain name to our server, if you would like to use Zsite service.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Login Zsite and click \"My Site\". You will see a red exclamation mark to remind you that your site name is not resolved yet.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201510/f_47cfdeb945da4467f75e4499118f7c98.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Login the control panel of your site.Take DNSPOD as an example.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201510/f_9977e49f43765163b708e16b01b04fe5.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>1. Login DNSPOD backend.</p>\n<p>2. Click \"Add a record\".</p>\n<p>3. Put www in Host Record, CNAME in Record Type, and n1.zsite.com in Record Value. Then click \"Save\".</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Note:</p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">Do NOT resolve A record. <span style=\"color:#000000;\">A record is binding with the IP address of our server. If the IP address is changed and A record needs to be resolved, it would be troublesome to change that IP address. If we resovle CNAME record, we do not have to worry about IP address.</span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">If your site was not registered with www, leave host record blank when resolve CNAME.</span><br />\n</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>','article',116,',1,116,145,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-30 09:26:39','2016-11-02 13:12:24',64,3,'en'),(146,'Why my site is locked?','lockedsite','site;locked','','<p>When you create a site on Zsite, your identity is not required for your convenience. All you have to do is to login with a registered account or third party account. However, you have to submit your profile for identity verification within three days after that. When the verification is done, you can use our online service. Your site will be locked if you do not submit it for verification.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Let\'s see how you can verify your identity.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Login Zsite. If you have not submitted your profile, there will be a notice telling you that you have to verify your identity,</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201309/430ecdfc05a6685676bc2aa249a33ad4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Click \"Submit identity verification\", and a window will pop out for you to fill in your information. Check \"I have read and acknowledged Zsite Agreement\" and click \"Save\". We will verify your application as soon as possible.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201309/fabca1d2b7bed50be8863f03bef2bbe8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>','article',116,',1,116,146,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-08-30 09:26:39','2016-08-30 10:19:02',79,4,'en'),(147,'Zsite data backup','','','','','article',116,',1,116,147,',3,'tengfei','','2016-08-30 09:26:39','2016-08-30 09:32:55',86,5,'en'),(148,'Changer Pro Manual','changerpro','','','','book',0,',148,',1,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 10:16:10','2016-11-14 16:00:17',0,148,'en'),(149,'Function','','','','<p>Changer Mall Pro is developed for E-commerce users. Its main functions include</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<ul><li>Product attributions set by category</li>\n<li>Price set by product attribution</li>\n<li>Customized search conditions by attribution</li>\n<li>SMS notification</li>\n<li>Tracking product shipment<br />\n</li>\n</ul>','article',148,',148,149,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 10:16:23','2016-10-28 10:50:11',146,1,'en'),(150,'Installation','','','','<p>Changer Mall Pro is encrypted by zend guard, so zend guard loader has to be installed in your server before you install Changer.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>You can install Changer Mall Pro in two ways as following,</p>\n<p>1. Purchase extension at the backend of Changer and choose local installation;</p>\n<p>2. Download Changer Mall Pro installation package.</p>','article',148,',148,150,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 10:16:23','2016-10-28 10:53:14',50,2,'en'),(151,'Product','','','','','chapter',148,',148,151,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 10:16:23','2016-10-28 10:53:27',0,3,'en'),(152,'Work Sheet','','','','','chapter',148,',148,152,',2,'tengfei','','2016-10-28 10:16:23','2016-10-28 10:18:19',0,4,'en'),(153,'SMS Notification','','','','<p>Changer Mall Pro integrates SMS notificatioin. You can set SMS interface at the backend, and then use it to send shipping notification, new order notification, etc.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"Settings\"-&gt;\"Site\" and switch on the SMS notification function.</p>','article',148,',148,153,',2,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 10:16:23','2016-10-28 13:46:55',50,5,'en'),(154,'Product Attribution','','','','<p>Product attribution can be customized in Changer Mall Pro.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"Mall\"-&gt;\"Settings\", and you can see the page to set attributions for Product. Attributions that can be customized can used to set search conditions and to calculate product prices.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>When add a product. choose attributions you set.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Check your product at the frontend/webpage.</p>','article',151,',148,151,154,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 10:53:34','2016-10-28 10:57:47',85,1,'en'),(155,'Product Price','','','','<p>Product price in Changer Mall Pro can be set by attribution, so it will be flexible to use.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Go to \"\"Mall\"-&gt;\"Product\", and set Price by attributions.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Price will be calculated by attributions a customer chooses at the front end.</p>','article',151,',148,151,155,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 10:53:34','2016-10-28 11:00:56',87,2,'en'),(156,'Settings','','','','<p>Work sheet in Changer Mall Pro is to facilitate conmmunications between you and your customers.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>There are three types of work sheet in Settings page.</p>\n<ul><li>General: your can customize work sheets;<br />\n</li>\n<li>By product category: set by product categories<br />\n</li>\n<li>By product: set by published products</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\"Service Period\" is the guarantee during which you will provide aftersales service. Within it, your customers can submit a work sheet to consult about any problems they have about the product. On the settings page, you can set the default period of the aftersales service, and set service period to certain customer/product.</p>','article',152,',148,152,156,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 11:03:43','2016-10-28 13:20:42',75,1,'en'),(157,'Submit and Manage a Worksheet','','','','<p><strong>Submit a worksheet</strong></p>\n<p>Login Changer Mall Pro, and go to \"My Worksheet\". You will see the list of your worksheet.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_9b3dae330ab0fc5fb4df683a1a3b46ce.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Click Create to add a worksheet.</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p><strong>Manage a worksheet</strong></p>\n<p>Go to backend of Changer, you can manage submitted worksheets, and reply, assign, or close it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201607/f_710400941da0669d3712717f830bfb76.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>There are three types of worksheet status, Pending, Replied and Closed.</p>','article',152,',148,152,157,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 11:03:43','2016-11-02 16:44:37',92,2,'en'),(158,'Customer Management','','','','You can manage all customeres by going to \"Worksheet\"-&gt;\"Customer\". Once a order is placed on the frontend/website, the related customer information will be automatically collected and saved at the backend.<br />','article',152,',148,152,158,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 11:03:43','2016-10-28 13:44:32',82,3,'en'),(159,'FAQ Management','','','','Frequently Asked Questions, aka FAQ, can be managed at Changer backend. Go to \"Worksheet\"-&gt;\"FAQ\", you can add and record the questions frequently asked anf their solutions.<br />','article',152,',148,152,159,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 11:03:43','2016-10-28 13:46:36',87,4,'en'),(161,'Choose Encryption','','','','<p>Changer encrypted tempates (which is purchased from Changer official website) will need to be decrypted before you use it. There are two ways to encrypt,</p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>1. zend guard loader</p>\n<p>It fits the situationyour space and virtual host that have zend guard loader, or your runtime can install it.(PHP TS cannot install it.) Please refert to <a href=\"http://changerpress.com/book/changermanual/162.html\" target=\"_blank\">4.3 Install zend guard loader</a></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>2. ioncube</p>\n<p>It fits the situation Changer, Ranger, or ZenTao one-click installation packages that have ioncube, or your runtime cannot install zend guard. Please refert to <a href=\"http://changerpress.com/book/changermanual/160.html\" target=\"_blank\">4.4 Install ioncube</a></p>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>Check Encryption</p>\n<ol><li>Create a new php file and write &lt;?php phpinfo()?&gt;.</li>\n<li>Save it to the root directory of your website and access this file via browser.</li>\n<li>On Configuration page, it will show all the extensions installed.</li>\n<img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201609/f_2d762f8cdee862cf6465b6d70f6bc0e4.png\" alt=\"\" /></ol>','article',7,',1,7,161,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 14:54:40','2016-10-31 08:14:29',70,6,'en'),(162,'Install Zend Guard Loader','','','','<p>Changer encrypted template (which is purchased on Changer official website) will need Zend Guard Loader to decrypt it. <span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.1429px;font-size:14px;\">Zend Guard Loader only support PHP NTS in </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Windows, so you need to install <strong>PHP NTS</strong> and <strong>fastcgi </strong>to anaylse PHP script<strong>.</strong></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><br />\n</strong></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Follow the steps to install Zend Guard Loader.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">1. Download Zend Guard Loader at <a href=\"http://www.zend.com/en/products/loader/downloads\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zend.com/en/products/loader/downloads</a> according to your own OS and PHP. If login is r e q u i r ed, you can \nuse this account chanzhi@cnez.uu.me and the password is 123456.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">2. Unzip and abstract ZendGuardLoader.so or ZendLoader.dll (Windows). Upload it to your server and grant permissions to run it.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">3. Add following codes to load <span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Zend Guard Loader</span></span>.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; For Linux and Mac OS X, use zend_extension = full path/ZendGuardLoader.so<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; For Windows (non-thread-safe), use&nbsp; zend_extension = full path/ZendLoader.dll</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">4. Add zend_loader.enable = 1 to&nbsp;php.ini to enable&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Zend Guard Loader</span></span></span></span>.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">5. <span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">If <span style=\"color:#E53333;\">ioncube loader</span> is applied, please make sure that you enable it before Zend guard \nLoader. If you use Apcache and cannot start Changer, please disable \nopcache and run Changer again.</span></span><span style=\"background-color:#FFE500;\"></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">6.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Restart Web server. If you use php-fpm, restart php-fpm as well. </span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">7. Print phpinfo(). If you can see the screeshot below, you have successfully installed <span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Zend guard Loader.</span></span><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n How to print phpinfo(): creat a new php file in your website root \ndirectory, and the content is &lt;?php phpinfo()?&gt;. Use a browser to \ncheck this file to see PHP info.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img src=\"http://www.chanzhi.org/data/upload/201602/f_77bdf8e6b889cdcaa5ad4ed8e152ec7b.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Codes needed to be added to <span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">php.ini </span></span><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; For Linux and Mac OS X</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\">zend_extension=\"/usr/lib/php/modules/ZendGuardLoader.so\"  （替换成自己的ZendGuardLoader.so路径）\nzend_loader.enable=1\nzend_loader.disable_licensing=0\nzend_loader.obfuscation_level_support=3</pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; For Windows</span><p><br />\n</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> </span></span></p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\">zend_extension=\"c:/php/ZendLoader.dll\"  （替换成自己的ZendLoader.dll路径）\nzend_loader.enable=1\nzend_loader.disable_licensing=0\nzend_loader.obfuscation_level_support=3</pre>\nNow you have installed <span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:25.1429px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Zend guard Loader</span></span></span></span>. You can set up Changer themes and Changer Pro plug-ins.<p><br />\n</p>','article',114,',1,114,162,',3,'tengfei','tengfei','2016-10-28 14:56:12','2016-10-28 14:57:24',69,3,'en');
